text: This one-of-a-kind contemporary home will not disappoint with its modern style and intelligent architecture for natural light capture throughout the day. Nestled in an idyllic setting amongst towering trees in peaceful Sudden Valley, enjoy amazing views and sounds of nature from inside and outside the house, with sunset colors gleaming over the hill and bathing the walls during golden hour. Featuring cathedral height ceilings, this immaculately cared for home is minutes away from hiking, golfing, biking, and lakefront access. The views from the primary bedroom and bathroom are the stuff dreams are made of. Experience luxurious living in a serene setting with space to entertain and relax, while the forested canopy keeps the home cool.

Tri-Level home with a great floor plan, nice flow and vaulted ceilings. Covered front porch offers views of the forest. The house sits in the middle of a double lot, so there is plenty of neighbor separation. All the rooms are large. Downstairs room is the biggest and could easily be a rec room. Primary bedroom has ensuite with 2 sinks and walk-in closet. Back patio off of the kitchen offers private place to enjoy the property. Large garage an long driveway for plenty of parking. enormous amount of dry storage area under the home.

Intimate & unobstructed stunning water view in this two-bedroom waterfront cabin tucked in close to the beach (stairs from the yard lead to an excellent crabbing & clamming beach!). This stout home was completely remodeled in 2005. Wood built-ins, bamboo floors, Anderson wood-wrapped window wall & french doors lead to a deck & a million dollar view of Mt. Baker, Hales Passage, & Canadian mountains. Additionally, there is a detached building with w/ an artist studio/workshop AND a guest suite with three-quarter bath which both take advantage of the view. Lovely terraced yard with enough space to grow your own vegetables, flowers and herbs.One car garage & off-street parking. Excellent location close to everything.Downsize without compromise!
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Ferndale School District, Lummi Elementary School

text: Fabulous Beachfront getaway in Birch Bay Village, PNW Premier 24/7 Guard gated Marina & Golf community. First time on market & loaded with character. T&G wood interior & updated kitchen, vaulted ceilings & room for everyone w/3 bedroom + sleeping loft. Large window walls capture vistas of the Bay & straight ahead breathtaking view of Mt. Baker & Cascades mountain range. Irreplicable footprint & full width shoreline concrete bulkhead. Step off your backyard & explore miles of sandy beachcombing. Great Blue Herons & Eagles abound & walking distance to private golf course, community clubhouse, Pickleball, Tennis & Basketball courts. Long list of Birch Bay Village clubs & year round activities, dog park, boat launch & more. Hurry on this one!

Welcome to this wonderful opportunity to own a gorgeous home site in Birch Bay. Bordering Birch Bay State Park, this property has everything you need to start building, including sewage, power, and water on-site. This fully fenced property features a shed and an additional building with a plumbed bathroom, along with a gazebo, making the property extremely usable.There are two RV hookups on the property, perfect for your recreational vehicle. A large portion of the property is covered with gravel for easy use and maintenance. This is an excellent opportunity to purchase a ready-to-enjoy property with great potential to become a home site, including the possibility of an ADU adjacent to the home.

This 2bed/1.75ba home is located in one of the finest cul-de-sacs in Sudden Valley's Gate 1. This adorable home has a fully updated kitchen w/ solid cherry cabinets & granite counters, new mini split, washer/dryer, generator installed & connected to breaker box, new paint inside and out & a beautifully landscaped front yard and fully fenced backyard. Spend your evenings out on the large deck overlooking the 15th fairway and greenspace or take a short walk down to the marina and dog park. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own your own private oasis in Sudden Valley's best neighborhood!

WOW This gorgeous Historic FAIRHAVEN condo now available & priced to sell. Featuring soaring ceilings making it feel way larger than the square footage would lead. Entire wall of built-ins including the queen Murphy bed, custom kitchen cabinets, stainless steel appliances & shelving, custom lighting with dimmers, window treatments, tall french doors open to the Juliet balcony that brings the outside in, laminate flooring, ceiling fan, laundry closet, & more. The building also includes a community rooftop deck/patio/lounge area with views in all directions. This unit comes with THREE PARKING spots too. ALL this in the heart of Fairhaven, with an elevator down to amazing dining, and shops, or walk to waterfront parks, ferry terminal, and more

Welcome to 410 Fieldston Road in beautiful Bellingham, WA! This charming home offers 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms within its 2900 square feet of living space. Enjoy breathtaking bay and island views from the comfort of your own home. The property is ideally situated just minutes from Old Historic Fairhaven, allowing you to easily access the area's shops, restaurants, and entertainment offerings. Nestled in the sought-after Edgemoor neighborhood, this home provides a perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. With its spacious layout and stunning views, this residence is an ideal retreat for those seeking the quintessential Bellingham lifestyle. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your own!

Only 4 min to Fairhaven...this fabulous 3BR, 3BA custom home is ready for new owners with breathtaking views of Chuckanut Bay! Built for entertaining and highly recreational, the showstoppers are your massive top floor deck with incredible scenery & ground level patio, perfect for entertaining or enjoying a stunning sunset PLUS direct access to the acclaimed Interurban Trail right from your back porch making this the perfect PNW adventure home! Additional features include tons of windows throughout for plenty of natural light & bay views, 3 car garage w/finished floors, add'l storage room, wood floors, vaulted ceilings, two living spaces, fully fenced yard w/stunning landscaping, metal roof and so much more! A must experience!

Help! I was a great looking home when I was built in '62 but unfortunately I was left all alone a few years back & I haven't been the same since. I'm perched on a pretty good sized lot & within walking distance to amazing Maple Beach. At my heart is a cozy fireplace to gather around & I provide 2 bedrooms & a full bathroom. I even have a new skylight that wasn't exactly planned but you can now stargaze through the roof! I'm a bit saggy on the right hand side. Looking for a long term relationship with a new owner to bring me back to my good old self or better! I'm gonna be a lot of work but hopefully a rewarding experience. Call my great broker to discuss. PS... I'm offered up at way below assessed value to make me more interesting!

Beautiful Residential building lot tucked away in the Samish Neighborhood. The property is located at the northeast corner of the intersection of Dumas Avenue and Ashley Street, both full width rights of way; there is an undeveloped plated alley right of way to the east of the property. The property is covered in grasses, native vegetation and trees. There is an existing garage located off the alley access to the east. There are no identified critical areas (wetlands, streams, habitat areas or steep slopes) on the property Water, gas and electricity are in the street. The main sewer line is close by on Ashley St and development of the lot would require connection. Easy access to I-5, downtown and everything Bellingham has to offer.

This property offers a rare opportunity to own nearly 10 acres of versatile land in a highly desirable location on the Guide Meridian. While the existing house requires significant renovation, the expansive lot provides ample space for various uses, the possibilities are endless. This property features a large detached garage as well as a 2200 sq. ft. shop to store just about anything you want. Currently the owners are getting paid $3, 500/year to advertise for a company on their large billboard on the property.

Affordable bungalow nestled in the scenic Sudden Valley community. This unique home features vaulted ceilings and a wall of windows that enhances the cozy cabin-in-the-woods feel. The basement includes laundry and ample space for storage. Step outside to a large deck that overlooks Strawberry Falls Trail and Creek, offering immediate access to outdoor adventure. Spacious driveway with plenty of room for parking. Enjoy all of the amenities that this community has to offer such as a golf course, community beaches, pool, marina, athletic courts and more. Whether you are a first time home buyer or looking for an investment, you don't want to miss out on this one-of-a kind property!

Large Lot, over 1/3 Acre within the controlled subdivision of Ocean View Estates. Lot is located in a quiet cul-de-sac complete with curbs and sidewalks. Private Beach Access, West facing back yard backing onto a canal. Terrific building lot for that long await dream home. Be sure to check out Facts and Features for a virtual tour of the lot and area.

Back on the market, buyer got cold feet! Come check out this wonderful manufactured home in the Robin Lane 55+ highly sought after community. This lovely home is within walking distance to Fairhaven Park and an extensive network of trails. This Home is ready for your updates, finishing touches and is priced to sell fast with these in mind. This home boasts a spacious living room and primary bedroom with walk-in closet and 3/4 bath. Covered front deck, where you can enjoy your morning coffee and covered carport and two sheds on the property for optimal storage. Home to be sold AS IS, but bring your offers!

Discover the charm of this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bath rambler, with a recent kitchen remodel and ready for you to move in. Located within walking distance to schools and a park, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Key features include air conditioning-installed in 2023 and a water filtration system. The exterior was painted in 2023. Outside, enjoy a private backyard with a 15' by 6' shed, perfect for storage or hobbies. All three bedroom have new carpeting. The property behind the home is a greenbelt adding to the outdoor enjoyment! This home is a must-see for anyone seeking a move-in ready property in a prime location. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity!

Beautiful building lot at the dead end of quiet N Cedar Park Dr. This lightly treed lot is partially fenced, has a full culvert, storage shed and an approved 3 bedroom Glendon Biofilter septic design and permit. This is the perfect lot for your future dream home!

Welcome to your cozy haven in the heart of convenience! Step into this meticulously maintained 2-bed, 1.75-bath home and you will be greeted by spacious vaulted ceilings and an abundance of natural light streaming though the bay windows, French doors and skylights. Ample closets, cabinet space and a handy shed outside ensure you have room for all of your treasures. Embrace peace of mind with recent upgrades including fresh interior paint & new roof, furnace & ductwork installed in 2023. Enjoy access to fantastic amenities in this 55+ community including clubhouse with kitchen for special events, pool tables, and salon by appointment. Easy access to the bus line, I5, Fred Meyer, Whole Foods, Woods Coffee & more, making errands a breeze.

Sea Links at Birch Bay. One of the last remaining building lots within the gated community of Sea Links. Fully Serviced Lot. Water, Sewer & Power are in the Street. Ready to build. This could be the perfect opportunity in a growing area with few lots available. The Water/Sewer Hook-up fee is approx $9, 000 which includes the meter, permit & connection fee.

The perfect charming bungalow, nestled in the sought after Broadway Park neighborhood. This gem has been updated over the years with the intention of maintaining the character of the classic 1920's architecture. Large skylights bathe the home in natural light and a Murphy bed in the second bedroom creates versatility and added space. Situated on a corner lot, this home offers both a spacious garage and additional covered carport parking. The enchanting and private secret garden provides a serene outdoor retreat. The nearby Broadway and Cornwall Parks, Rose Garden, shopping, hospital and top-rated Parkview Elementary enhance the appeal of this prime location.

Impeccable Home on the Hill that was completely remodeled from top to bottom by current owners. Located on dead end street. Spectacular views of Mt Baker, Bellingham, San Juan's, & even Mt Rainer on a clear day! 3228 sqft of living area, 3 Beds & 3 Baths w fully finished 528sf 2 Car Garage. Large 19, 602 sf lot, w room for Shop or further expansion. All new SS Appliances! This home also features AC, On Demand H20, 4 Hose Bibs 1 w Hot/Cold feature. Spacious lawn area w mature landscaping, a water feature, Nat Gas fire pit + large East facing deck w expansive views! Shed in backyard stays. Huge concrete stamped driveway w extra parking.

Experience quintessential American living in the heart of Lynden w/this beautiful 3 bdrm home. This floor plan gives many options for a variety of lifestyles. Upstairs, 2 bdrms are complemented by stunning Pottery Barn inspired bathrooms. The huge bedroom is plumbed for a gas FP.Head downstairs & enjoy the finished basement w/bar, potential wine closet, & MORE...perfect for watching your favorite game or classic movie in a beautifully appointed media masterpiece.Then step out onto the covered back porch to enjoy the hot tub & fully fenced backyard w/alley access. Addt'l parking & convenient carport also await. Whether ithe charm of day to day living or entertaining indoor & out, don't miss out on this charming slice of Americana.

Welcome to a centrally located, charming 1940's farmhouse on a perfect piece of property! A rare find in this market! This 3 bedroom 2 bath home features all main floor living with a large living/family room and a potential bonus upstairs upon finishing the attic. Ample natural light abounds throughout a smooth floorpan making this home very inviting. Primary bedroom includes his and hers closets. Multiple well kept outbuildings including barn and a shop with a work space on almost 3 acres offer opportunity for a small homestead, hobby farm or simply a little extra space while only minutes from Bellingham, Lynden or the freeway. This perfect property won't last long!

Located in an exceptional neighborhood near top-rated schools and beautiful Whatcom Falls Park, this charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home offers convenient access to Lake Whatcom. The home features a spacious deck perfect for entertaining, overlooking a private, fenced backyard teeming with birds and wildlife. The interior is clean and move-in ready, boasting modern amenities and ample living space. The beautifully landscaped front and back yards enhance the home's curb appeal, providing a serene and inviting outdoor environment. Don't miss this opportunity to live in a vibrant community with natural beauty.

Your dream home awaits! This charming rambler offers 3 bedrooms + a versatile rec room/potential 4th BR, perfect for a starter or forever home. Updated kitchen w/ new cabinets features pantry, ample counter space & a convenient dining area. Spacious primary bedroom faces the backyard & is filled w/light. Curl up by the fireplace in the living room or enjoy coffee on your back patio. Updates include NEW carpet, interior & exterior paint, roof & septic system. Nestled on a spacious 1-acre lot w/ a 24x24 barn/shop w/open stalls, garden beds & fruit trees - your hobby farm awaits. Plenty of parking & just a short jaunt from Bellingham or Lynden, this home is the perfect blend of comfort & convenience.

Most adorable Beach Cottage ever on 50 feet of west facing waterfront! Sweeping views of Mt Baker to the east and the San Juan Islands and Salish Sea to the west. 2 bedrooms (one with Murphy Bed) and 1 fabulously updated full bath. Gorgeous finishes throughout, quartz countertops, hardwood flooring, wood built-ins galore, gas fireplace, Air Conditioning, heat pump, & mini-split. Vaulted ceiling, big wall of windows and French Doors to appreciate the sparkling blue ocean & the beach. Expansive entertainment deck and firepit on the beach. Detached garage for 1 car and plenty of additional storage space, plus off-street parking. Don't miss this opportunity to own a little piece of heaven on the beach!

Investors, anyone looking to enjoy the downtown Bellingham lifestyle, this is the one for you! Sip coffee on your private balcony as you people-watch above the tree-lined pedestrian zone connecting Fairhaven to downtown Bellingham. Secured lobby entrance, up a few stairs or take the elevator! Clean, bright 1 bed, 1 bath unit just steps from restaurants/shopping, and within walking distance of WWU. You'll enjoy the large storage closets in the bedroom and cozying up by the fireplace in the open-concept living area. Plenty of room for an in-home office workspace, too. Gated, underground parking ensures your vehicle is safe and easily accessible by elevator. No rental cap in this complex! You won't want to miss this downtown gem.
neighborhoods: Downtown District Bellingham, City Center Bellingham

Forested, private, with Deer Creek on property, one acre - set back & distant from corner of Northwest & Axton Roads w/ private easement that leads to home - Huff Way. Mid-Century tri-level home - large front yard w/lots of parking & sunny, park-like back yard & 3-car garage almost 800 SF. Built 1958, 1, 848 SF, 3 BR & 1.75 BA w/hardwood floors. Close to I-5 & Bellingham shopping - COSTCO etc. A lot is going on at this home - location, forested feel in front & back, Mid-Century style + more!

Step into the latest new construction home in Kamm Creek, where modern design meets comfort. This thoughtfully designed one level residence features an open-concept kitchen with top-quality stainless steel appliances, elegant quartz countertops, custom cabinetry, and a generously sized central island ideal for entertaining. Outside, the oversized covered patio overlooks the dedicated Kamm Creek open space, creating a perfect spot for enjoying outdoor meals and entertainment.

Serene country living in this stunning home on a picturesque 3.8-acre lot. The kitchen boasts tile countertops, pine cabinets, lots of storage in an open pantry, & nearly new appliances. Separate dining room. Partially fenced w/two sheds & a private firepit area. And the 20 x 35 foot shop is a game changer in this price range.

Nice homes in this waterfront neighborhood.

Presenting 1795 Pangborn, a beloved home now on the market for the first time in 50 years. This charming property boasts 2, 390 SF of living space, featuring 4 bedrooms and 1.75 bathrooms. Step inside to discover an inviting open floor plan, highlighted by a spacious living room with lots of natural light, large dining area and a family room with a cozy wood stove. Beyond the main residence, the property offers lots of outbuildings, including storage buildings, a nice sized shop, and a picturesque barn complete with a large hay loft. Sitting on 8 acres of prime farmland with irrigations rights, this is a truly unique opportunity to own your own piece of county paradise.

Experience the best of both worlds: enjoy the tranquility of country living on an acre while being just minutes away from local amenities. This stunning single-level home w/ a basement has it all. The property boasts a freshly painted exterior. Remodeled kitchen has an island, walk-in pantry, soft close cabinets, and vaulted ceilings that flow nicely into the living room. Large primary bedroom has vaulted ceilings & walk-in closet. The garage offers 2 oversized parking spots, ample storage space, & a loft above for additional versatility. The back yard features cherry, pear, & apple trees, along with blueberry plants. Don't miss this unique opportunity to own a beautifully updated home with abundant space & charming outdoor amenities.

Location, location, location! Highly desirable neighborhood w/wide streets, spacious lots & well-kept homes. Sprawling rambler sitting on a lush & generous 14, 375sqft lot. A gardener's dream, surrounded by beautiful mature plantings, trees, privacy, & raised beds. The over-sized primary suite has room for a creative setting, & includes separate jetted tub/shower, & walk-in closet. The great room is also spacious w/cozy fireplace, vaulted ceilings, & a wall of windows that frame the inviting & fully fenced private backyard. Need a 4th bedroom, den or? Use the generously sized office w/built-in custom cabinets for your needs. Everyone will appreciate the hard-to-find 830sqft 3+ car garage! Room for cars, toys & storage. Call for a tour today!

Tucked away in the heart of the Meridian School District, this spacious mid-century home sits on nearly an acre and offers peace and seclusion. Located at the end of a shaded, private lane, you are sure to discover your PNW haven. Lots of recent upgrades including central AC, fresh interior and exterior paint, brand-new carpet in 2 bedrooms, a freshly remodeled bathroom, an updated kitchen, fresh attic insulation, and a tankless water heater. The large backyard creates a perfect setting for play and relaxation, just add a hot tub to the existing pad. From the home, you'd never know you're just 10 minutes from I-5, Ferndale, Lynden, and Bellingham, and just steps from downtown Laurel. Your peaceful and move-in-ready retreat awaits you!

Come build your new home in beautiful Sudden Valley! This flat, double lot is perfect for your new home. Included with this property is the survey and Builder plans which include a single story home and 3 car garage. Sudden Valley is known for its close proximity to Lake Whatcom which makes it a great place to live full time or a great vacation destination. Amenities included a 18 hole championship golf course, marina, pools, gym, trails, beaches and more!

NEW 4 BEDROOM HOME at the Ridge in Blaine. This home along Oleander Drive is located north of the new Harbor Hills Parkway in the East Maple Ridge Development. Buy a new home at the beginning of its life and avoid the wear, tear and maintenance of an older home. Large open living area with 10' ceilings on the main floor, fireplace and vinyl plank flooring, open living, dinning and kitchen area gives you the feeling of a much larger space. Cabinets covered with beautiful quartz countertops. Enjoy a large covered patios in the back yard along a wooded greenbelt. Large bonus room above the finished garage with an outline for EV charging. A short drive to town, I-5 or the Canadian Border. 20 minutes commute to Bellingham.

Incredible Location! Prime Horse Property at the End of a paved road. Expansive views. The Beauty of Open Skies...Corn Fields in the summer... Flocks of Snow Geese in Winter...Nothing compares! 4 stall horse barn (w/heated tack room, washer/dryer hook up & heated office w/half bath). Potential ADU (separate entrance, natural gas fireplace, separate AC/furnace, washer/dryer hook up, tankless hot water system). Large storage shed with lean-to. Garden shed. Main house has new furnace & AC (May 2023). New WEll Pump (Aug.2022). Water purification System. Gentran hookup in garage. ADT security system. Large patio with fire-pit. Natural gas fireplace. 3 car garage.

North Whatcom County rolling 4+ acres with tons of trees, Open Space and Fields. Blaine mailing Address - Lynden School district. Roughly 1/2 way in-between Blaine and Lynden off H Street Road. Property is serviced by Power. Buyer will need to install Septic and a Well. Excellent property - Priced for immediate sale.

Stunning, sophisticated and serene! Located in highly sought after Birch Bay Village on a very quiet street with fully fenced private backyard & expansive trex deck for entertaining. Enter into this single level split floorplan for the ultimate in turn-key living. Recent remodel includes flooring, paint, fixtures, fireplace, guest bath and more! Vaulted ceilings, skylights, radiant floors in primary bath, stainless package, tons of storage, oversized garage and plenty of room for RV/boat parking! Grab your golf cart and enjoy the lifestyle in BBV with private beaches, parks, marina, golf, clubhouse, pickleball, social activities & 24 security gate! It truly does not get any better than this- no projects and plenty of time to play!

Stunning Contemporary Home w/private lake access & new community dock! Experience all four seasons on the lake. Enjoy breathtaking Lake Whatcom & rolling foothill views from nearly every room. Entertain w/ease in a dream chef's kitchen featuring two ovens & tons of space. Relax on two spacious decks or hot tub w/ lake views. Top floor 1, 000 sqft primary suite includes fireplace, tiled walk-in shower, jacuzzi tub & large walk-in closet. Stunning sunrises & sunsets from upper deck. Lower level: living room, theatre room, 2 bedrooms & bonus space. Great option for multi-generational space or renting for extra income! Garage w/ extra loft & storage. Tons of parking. Removable fence for pets. End of street w/Stimson Reserve hiking trail access.

Country retreat on expansive grounds with a short trail to the Nooksack River. Just 20 minutes from Bellingham, and moments from Whatcom County's renowned eagle-watching spot. This maintained home has numerous recent upgrades, such as a newly renovated primary bedroom, generator, tankless water heater, and mini split heating and cooling systems for year-round comfort. Huge 2 bay garage with workshop and pellet stove. New exterior paint and roof done in 2021. Featuring a spacious living area, the home includes two additional downstairs bedrooms and a versatile office/sunroom adjacent to the kitchen. Ample space for gardening and accommodating farm animals, with outbuildings offering limitless possibilities for vehicle storage or hobbies.

Located on a quiet & private cul-de-sac, surrounded by mature cedars & perfectly situated on a beautifully landscaped 1/3-acre lot, this 4 bedroom residence is sure to please! Newly installed vinyl plank flooring greats you upon entry & showcases an an inviting living room w/ vaulted ceilings & cozy family room w/ gas fireplace. Bright & airy kitchen seamlessly connects to the newly constructed 16x20 enclosed Trex deck, taking full advantage of the park-like rear yard. The upper level consists of 4 generous bedrooms + a den each w/ adequate space that offers comfort & convenience. Other features include: the large 3-car garage, new roof/gutters (2022), & fresh paint throughout. All within walking distance to the golf club & other amenities.

Welcome to this charming 3-bed, 2-bath home in Bellinghams sought-after Puget Neighborhood. Perched at the top of W Racine, at the end of a serene cul-de-sac, this residence boasts exquisite views that enhance its appeal. The large deck, sauna and expansive backyard are among the finest in the neighborhood, perfect for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. Inside, youll find tasteful updates including high-quality floors, new tiled shower and extra-large windows that flood the space with natural light. The extra-large 2-car garage features a work space, bike storage, and is plumbed for an additional bathroom and is car charge ready. New high-efficiency furnace provides lower cost heating and AC. This home is truly a Puget Hill gem!

Stunningly crafted home perfectly positioned on an expansive corner lot with custom features throughout. The open floor plan boasts cherry cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The main floor features extensive bamboo flooring, vaulted ceilings, a cozy gas fireplace, and a spacious patio ideal for entertaining. The primary suite on the main floor includes dual walk-in closets, a double tiled shower, and a luxurious jetted tub. Upstairs, find two additional bedrooms and a bonus room. The landscaped yard features a sports court, providing both beauty and functionality. Welcome to the essence of living in the highly sought-after Lynden neighborhood, where scenic walking trails and charming parks are just steps away.

You will love this clean, bright & open concept 3 bed, three-bath+ loft home minutes from the beach, clubhouse & boat launch! The main floor features two bedrooms; one a primary w/ full bath & a second bedroom + extra loft space (art/music studio/home office?). Brand new roof in 2021! Other updates include hand-scraped hardwood plank floors, tile, a brand-new front deck, + more. At ground level, with/ a separate exterior entrance, is a second primary bedroom w/ a 3/4 bath. An excellent short-term rental opportunity or overflow for your guests! A private backyard features terraced decks, gorgeous cedar, & fir trees, making it an oasis of calm. Go crabbing and exploring for the day from the boat launch & come home to this beautiful spot.

There is a bedroom on the main floor and flex space to use as you like in the large loft. The stand up crawl space has hook ups for a washer & dryer and room for storage. It's 7 minutes to beaches @Lake Whatcom and other amenities of the Sudden Valley community. 20 min to downtown Bellingham, 55 min to BC border & 2 hrs to Seattle. Take the stairs @ #4 on Lot 31, or follow the trail through separate buildable lot 32 which adds value & options & is included in the sale. You can combine lots & lower dues, or build a house, or a garage. 15, 172 total square feet both lots.

Unique waterfront Chartwell Estates Condominium.Feel like your on vacation every day! Sweeping views of Bay & San Juan Islands.Equipped with a gourmet kitchen and island, Thermador double oven, gas top burners with hood at island.Fine craftsmanship throughout.Master has a powder area and 4 piece bath.Recent engineered HW floors on main level, bathroom updates.Radiant floor heat on main level.Closets have organizers, stairs are lighted, and bathrooms and kitchen have lighting accents.Expansive grounds have a gazebo, garden areas, landscaping and greenbelt buffers.Separate furnished clubhouse ideal for gatherings. 8 min to Bellingham City Center. 90 min to Baker ski area. Area abounds with recreation and entertainment. A must see!

This remarkable home offers a comfortable living space featuring 4 beds and 2.5 baths. Inside, you'll find vaulted ceilings in both the living room and dining areas. floor-to-ceiling custom fireplace, open floor plan, spacious kitchen w/ island, pantry, mudroom, and laundry area, primary bedroom on the main floor w/walk-in closet. Other notable features of this property include a covered front porch, an entry closet, and a 2-car garage. Step outside onto the covered back porch w/ a privacy wall for those who love outdoor entertaining, perfect for year-round gatherings. Don't miss out on this opportunity. House plan model - Lexington. Photos are for example purposes but are not the actual house

Experience PNW year round, at this beautiful at Snowater Resort. Endless amenities to create lifelong memories. Endless trails throughout the complex, Nooksack river, Mt. Baker National Forest, you've got access to every outdoor activity you can imagine! This condo is turn-key with everything you could possibly need included! Use as your private getaway, vacation home, or rental. Snowater Resort has popular amenities, such as two indoor pools/hot tubs, a sauna, indoor sports courts, tennis, two playgrounds, a gym, lounge areas, picnic areas, outdoor BBQs, & so much more. Let this be the recreational or investment property that continues for generations! End unit, wood fireplace, up/down blinds, buy today, and start your vacation tomorrow!

Amazing estate property with so much potential to create your dream home, with gated access to the neighborhood, future Canadian Rocky views and the ultimate in privacy. Owners have plans in hand to build an estate home, so you can capitalize on their legwork or start on your own dream! Most of the lots are still owned by the original developer with no plans to sell in the near future. There's a forestry plan in place that will allow several acres to be cleared to capitalize on the views and create a nice open building site with lots of natural light. You don't want to miss out on this amazing 20 acre lot!

This stunning custom home has it all! Grand 2-story entry w/office, open floor plan with spacious living rm and gas fireplace, dining room & kitchen with granite counters, ss appls & walk-in pantry. Main floor features beautiful hardwood floors throughout! Patio doors open to large deck for entertaining and just steps away to the Hot tub and fenced backyard. Huge primary bedroom with double door entry, fully tiled walk-in shower, jetted tub, double vanity & walk-in closet. 2 more bedrooms + bonus room upstairs. Daylight basement is perfect for entertaining w/ a Theater room, wet bar, rec room, sauna and 4th Bd w/ensuite bath. 2-car garage +workshop area, shed in backyard and in-ground sprinkler system. Call today for your private viewing!

GALBRAITH Mountain & LAKE PADDEN Lovers, Investors, Dream Home Builders, here is the basecamp you've been searching for! Nearly 5 acres of PRIME real estate. Move right into the updated 1390sf, 3-bed 1.75 bath Manuf. Home w/huge sun deck & extra storage room. Keep the toys & do all your projects in the 28X40 SHOP w/workbenches, 448sf storage loft & mechanic's pit! Rent the 2nd, older Manuf. Home on a 4BR septic + separate elec. meter while you design your custom dream home. Both homes served by a private, semi-artesian well. The property shares a corner with Galbraith's mountain bike trail mecca, for direct access. 26X38 steel equipment shed on a concrete slab & addl. bldgs. This is an exceptional opportunity for south side B'ham acreage.

Multigenerational living or passive income potential as lower level features 2BR, one with attached full bath and a small kitchenette. Located in the quiet yet convenient Puget neighborhood, this light and bright home is surprisingly private as it backs Whatcom Falls Park with peaceful sounds of the seasonal creek. The upstairs level of the home has vaulted ceilings, tons of natural light and very spacious primary suite. Walk out to the expansive double decker composite deck ready for everything from fabulous entertaining to peace and quiet surrounded by nature. Additional features include an oversize garage with extra tall ceiling great for car enthusiasts or additional storage. Close to shopping and a short walk to multiple trails.

Fantastic four bedroom, two bath home on huge lot with peek a boo water views. This updated home is well kept, has two large living spaces and a giant level lot. Main living space has open layout, huge deck overlooking the backyard and large bedrooms with a full bath. Lower level has many possibilities, with its own large living room, kitchen, bath and two bedrooms, could be a perfect mother in law space, additional family room or look into renting out. Located in the heart of Blaine, walkable to town and close to amenities, this home is a wonderful opportunity.

Perched at the top of the hill, this beautiful lightly treed double lot offers a gate-accessible building site with potential for astounding views of Bellingham and north to Canada! At 0.37ac, there is plenty of room for your imagination to manifest into the home of your dreams! Build a custom home, a home with a shop, or you could even put a manufactured home here. With public water and electricity available, all you need is a septic system to have utilities all setup. Sitting at the end of Jimi Hendrix Way, this lot offers ultimate privacy where you will be surrounded by a canopy of trees and abundant nature. Outside Bellingham city limits gives many options for how to use this property. This is the opportunity you've been waiting for!

Investor alert. This 3 bed, 1.5 bath fixer boasts 1285 sq feet and sits on a large .54 acre (23, 522 sq ft) lot. Ready to be rebuffed & brought to its original glory. Step inside to large living area w/ 2 fireplaces, rustic hardwood floors & sizable dining area. The kitchen features quartz countertops & stainless appliances. The primary bedroom features a cool loft area & high ceilings. Enjoy the comfort of heat pump/AC. Take advantage of the fully enclosed sunroom, deck, downstairs fully finished attached living quarters and the deck/firepit area w/bathroom down by the creek. Surrounded by fruit trees & the pristine beauty of nature. Double entry/horseshoe driveway. A stone's throw to Pine and Cedars trailhead & all Chuckanut has to offer.

Build your dream home on 5 serene acres with wide open gorgeous valley & mountain views w/ potential Squalicum Lake views. A private & gated paved driveway leads you to this beautiful & flat property with an existing private well and available water share. Acreage is fully fenced with a small grove of mature trees to the west. Homes above have natural gas & fiber optic internet service. 3 bed septic approved documents with country for 4 bedroom septic. Recent wetlands delineation & report completed. Well installed, Power Base installed, Private Road is Paved.

Great HUD Home in Maple Falls! Price Reduced! This newer home built in 2020 has 2 bedrooms, plus den/office & 2 baths, including nice primary bedroom with ensuite bath. Home features open concept design with open kitchen / dining area & spacious living room. Large, fully fenced yard with gated entry for extra security & privacy. Plenty of room to spread out. Located in Paradise Lakes area with mountain views. This home is in great shape and is ready for your special touches inside and out!

Gorgeous, single story home in desirable Lynden! Spacious and bright, this home has been updated with luxury vinyl plank, stainless appliances and a newer 30 yr roof and furnace. The no-steps entry welcomes you to this thoughtfully designed, 4 bed 3.25 bath home with room to spread out. Two generous living areas, large primary bedroom with bathroom and a bonus room conversion in the garage with separate entrance and ensuite 3/4 bathroom is the perfect studio, workspace, or guest room. A true entertainer's back yard, fully fenced and complete with concrete patio, fire pit area, and loads of privacy. Fantastic Lynden neighborhood close to schools and parks!

This ONE-LEVEL living beautiful craftsman 3bd 2ba home in a small community of 10 homes & a park is now available.You will fall in love entering the home with gorgeous interior designs featuring hardwood floors, thoughtful open kitchen/living space W/ granite counters, custom backsplash, stainless appliances and perfect kitchen island facing the amazing fireplace wall with custom mantle, shelving and tv/electronics area &wired for inwall speakers.Warm interior colors, custom ceiling fans, lighting, fixtures & high ceilings that make this home feel larger than the sq footage would lead.Screened-in/ covered back porch for entertaining looks out over the professionally landscaped grounds with green belt behind. Oversized two-car garage W /workspace

Glenhaven Gem! This wonderful 3bd 2bath home features open concept living with vaulted ceilings and a cozy pellet stove in the living room. The kitchen boasts a beautiful mosaic backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and a large primary bath with granite countertops and double sinks. Enjoy endless hot water with the on-demand water heater. Step outside to a spacious Trex deck and sunny, fully-fenced backyard with a shed and garden space. Recent updates include new flooring, trim, accent walls, light fixtures, and a remodeled primary bath with a jet tub. Other highlights are a 2019 metal roof, new 115' fence, and updated kitchen fixtures. Dont miss this fantastic rambler, with beach access, community center, and close to Bellingham.

Water and North Cascade Mountain View, Main floor living area bathed in sunlight, Built in 2017, 4 bedroom, 3.75 baths, plus private office, 3300 sq. ft. 3-level home with elevator, granite counters, engineered hardwood floors, elegant finishes, lots of closets, main floor living room, 2nd level family room, Central air conditioning, three decks give home lots of outdoor living space to enjoy the view and sunny days. Two seperate entrances. Unbelievable heated 6-8 car garage for all the toys(1700Sq.Ft.), with 1/2 bath, located 1/2 mile from salt water marina, lots of parking. Sandy Point Community Membership available if you choose. Amenities include, marina, golf course, clubhouse, swimming pool, sports courts & organized activities.
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Ferndale School District, Lummi Elementary School

text: Beautifully remodeled, 4-story Craftsman home in the heart of Bellingham. 3 bd & 2 ba offering spacious & versatile living. Open-concept kitchen & livingroom are the perfect spot for entertaining. There are 2 custom-built mini-offices, too! Closets have extensive built-in cabinetry. New tile in baths, a clawfoot tub, soft-close drawers, and an all-new kitchen! The full basement and attic remodel provide additional hang-out space. Outdoors, enjoy a playhouse/guest loft in the fully-fenced backyard, surrounded by lovely landscaping and berry bushes. Relax on your new back deck, huge covered front porch or your private patio equipped with hammock hooks. Bocce ball court or a great sun-filled spot for veggie boxes! Quick bike ride to downtown!
